{"word":"σχίζω","slug":"σχίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>σχίζω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Skt.\">Skt.</a>; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>σϰεδἁννυμι</el> ‘scatter’] ‘cause to be in parts through force’, <b>tear, rend<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of fabric: cloth or garment <b><a href='B:490 5:36'>Lk 5:36</a>; <a href='B:500 19:24'>J 19:24</a>;</b> fishing net <b><a href='B:500 21:11'>21:11</a>;</b> the temple veil, with specification: <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δύο\">δύο</a></el> in two <b><a href='B:470 27:51'>Mt 27:51a</a>; <a href='B:480 15:38'>Mk 15:38</a>;</b> <el>μέσον</el> <b><a href='B:490 23:45'>Lk 23:45</a>.</b> Of rock formation<b> <a href='B:470 27:51'>Mt 27:51b</a>.</b> Of the region of the sky <b><a href='B:480 1:10'>Mk 1:10</a>.</b> By <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of a group of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> divided in viewpoint <b><a href='B:510 14:4'>Ac 14:4</a>; <a href='B:510 23:7'>23:7</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:σχῆμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:σχίσμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}